FT  05 JUL 93 / UK Company News: Celsis share offer meets strong demand
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By RICHARD GOURLAY
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
The public offer of shares in Celsis International, the maker of diagnostic
equipment designed to replace and improve on the laboratory agar plate for
detection of microbes, was nearly four times subscribed.
Panmure Gordon said there had been applications totalling 27m shares for the
7m shares on offer at 100p.
