dividend in respect of 1992 since the associated advance corporation tax
would not be recoverable in the foreseeable future and consequently the net
asset value of the group would be reduced by more than the dividend amount -
20p was paid for 1991.
Pre-tax profits for 1992 fell from Pounds 20.2m to Pounds 14.1m on turnover
which slipped to Pounds 318.6m (Pounds 326.5m).
