<TEXT>
Somali gunmen killed three Italian soldiers and wounded 21 when they forced
800 Italian UN peacekeepers and 400 Somali police to retreat after a search
for illegal weapons in Mogadishu yesterday, Reuter reports from Mogadishu.
Lieutenant Colonel Giovanni Fiantini said the gunmen pinned down a convoy of
